</font></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ukaleido.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kaleido</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(4/18/01 1:42:02 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Resistance Suits</span><hr size=1> Well I went thru a rundown on Allakhazam and decided this is the gear I want. It will probably cost a fortune especially the enchanter made items but I guess I could spend a week kiting HG's for cash to get them. Anyway without any further todo....<br>
