</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uelawnah.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Elawnah</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_magentaspot.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(4/19/01 6:10:34 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.rasiel.com/wallpaper/paintings/640/dali2.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Resistance Suits</span><hr size=1> I have found that a full suit of Gnome Skin Armor really adds big time to your Posion resistance.I always toss that up when i am fighting something that likes to posion (dragons... necromancers... etc.) And, its pretty cheap, and easy to obtain. It drops in Tower of Frozen Shadow. (and possibly some other places)<br>
